@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@customerToken = paste-customer-token-here
@ownerToken = paste-owner-token-here
@driverToken = paste-driver-token-here
@orderId = paste-order-id-here

### Validation error example
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "menuItemId": "{{orderId}}",
      "quantity": 0
    }
  ]
}

### Invalid UUID parsing error example
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/not-a-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Customer orders with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/my?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Restaurant orders with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/restaurants/paste-restaurant-id-here?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

### Payment transactions with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/payments?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Driver deliveries with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/deliveries/my?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
